  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that was convincing enough, so I quickly went with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, for [NON-ENGLISH], we had to go out-- this was about an hour in Hungary, we knew when to come back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I walked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a beautiful fall day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I walked up to one of the main thoroughfares in Budapest, and thousands of people were walking up and down.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the evening, I asked my father that-- that how come these people who were walking up and down-- how do they live next year?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he explained it to me that you know, they are of different religion, and they don't have to do that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have to do other things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there are several religions, he said, just like there are several bookstores in Budapest, he said.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or even in Hungary, if somebody wants to buy the book, he does best if he buys it at Emil Kohn-- that was my father's name-- but there are books available at Fischer and [INAUDIBLE] and several other places.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, these are also books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are not bad books, but not as good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this is how he explained to me the difference between different religions-- a very practical approach.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
